articles.title: US shoots down Houthi missile aimed at American warship in Red Sea, officials say - ABC News
articles.description: The missile came from a Houthi-controlled area of Yemen, U.S. officials said.
articles.content:
A U.S. fighter aircraft shot down a missile fired toward an American warship from a Houthi-controlled area of Yemen, U.S. military officials said.
The USS Laboon was fired on in the Southern Red Sea… [+1441 chars]
